monthly_means <- ungroup(EOL_RAW) %>% 
  mutate(Month = format(datetime, format="%m")) %>% 
  group_by(Month) %>%
  summarise(
    Salinity_month = mean(salinity, na.rm = TRUE),
    Temperature_month = mean(temperature, na.rm = TRUE))
